CRFNAME: ADNI GO and ADNI 2: first batch analysis of CSF biomarkers
NOTES: *See 'ADNI GO and ADNI 2: first batch analyses of CSF biomarkers' Methods description for analytical details. NA: test results that did not meet pre-set analysis criteria of either (a) median fluoresence intensity values below that of the lowest calibrator; (b) bead counts below 50 for one or both of the duplicate samples; or, >25 % CV value for the duplicate samples. There was one sample that had MFI results below the lowest calibrator for each of the three biomarkers; there were 8 samples with bead counts below 50 for t-tau; there was 1 sample with %CV >25% for p-tau181.
